Version 3.3.30 - July, 2026
============================

New Features
------------

User Experience
+++++++++++++++

* **Modern Administration Navigation:** A new Left Navigation has been introduced for the Administration module, providing faster access to administrative features while aligning with the new Sparkflows user experience and navigation standards.

* **Project Workspace Navigation:** The Projects page has been enhanced with Recent Projects, Project Categories, and redesigned Project Cards, enabling quicker project access and improved navigation.

* **Workflow & Pipeline Editor Refresh:** The Workflow and Pipeline Editor now includes an enhanced editor canvas and refined node interface for a more intuitive and efficient workflow design experience.

Enhancements
------------

User Interface
++++++++++++++

* **Project Dashboard UI:** The Project Dashboard has been refreshed with modern card layouts, updated colors, and improved typography for a cleaner and more consistent user experience.

Co-Pilot
+++++++++

* **Co-Pilot Experience Improvements:** The Co-Pilot interface has been enhanced with an improved Prompt section, redesigned Response Preview, token usage visibility, and overall UI/UX refinements to streamline AI-assisted workflow creation.

Workflow Authoring
++++++++++++++++++

* **Workflow Node Anchors:** Support has been added for input and output anchors, enabling explicit Left/Right input mapping for multi-input nodes and improved handling of multiple outputs. This enhancement improves workflow readability, connection accuracy, and maintainability.


